title: Mod Info
go-to: flavors

Hello! This mod is inspired by Sericulture, a Roblox game (yes, really) by flowerofthewise. The worldbuilding is pretty awesome so I decided to use it. Most contributions to the lore are mine, though, as the actual game's lore is mainly a base and quite vague by design, to precisely allow people like me to go crazy with headcanons.